              }
            ],
            "subtype": "ability",
            "text": "If the boggard scout hits a creature with their tongue, that creature becomes grabbed by the boggard. Unlike with a normal Grab, the creature is not immobilized, but it can't move beyond the reach of the boggard's tongue. The DC to Escape is 18, or a creature can sever the tongue by hitting AC 13 and dealing at least 2 slashing damage. Though this doesn't deal any damage to the boggard, it prevents them from using their tongue Strike again until they regrow their tongue, which takes a week.",
            "type": "stat_block_section"
          },
          "name": "Tongue Grab",
